This project also helps understand how to detect malware:

Monitoring for unusual processes writing to files

Detecting DLL injection behavior (Meterpreter)

Reviewing connection logs for unknown outbound traffic

Using Windows Defender or Sysmon event logs

Behavioral detection via EDR tools

